  <div style="background:#1a1a1a;border:1px solid #2a2a2a;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;text-align:left;">
    <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#94a3b8;margin-bottom:16px;">วิธีเรียกเมนูใหม่</div>
